  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      KorAHF is a multi-center registry (prospective cohort) for acute decompensated heart failure
      patients in Korea.

      The aim of this registry is to analyze several causes affecting prognosis and survival and to
      develop new strategies for managing acute decompensated heart failure.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
